WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.667 --> 00:00:02.768
[monitor beeping steadily]

00:00:02.768 --> 00:00:06.038
[thunder booming]

00:00:06.038 --> 00:00:09.709
- HI, YOU MUST BE LIAM.

00:00:09.709 --> 00:00:13.679
- HEY, BUDDY,
HOW ARE YOU FEELING TODAY?

00:00:13.679 --> 00:00:17.250
- [hoarsely]
I'M FEELING FINE, DR. GUPTA.

00:00:17.250 --> 00:00:19.185
JUST FINE.

00:00:19.185 --> 00:00:20.586
- THIS IS MARION GLASS,

00:00:20.586 --> 00:00:22.722
AND SHE'S FROM
THE MAKE A WISH FOUNDATION.

00:00:22.722 --> 00:00:25.558
- MARION GLASS.

00:00:25.558 --> 00:00:27.961
- HOW ARE YOU
FEELING TODAY, LIAM?

00:00:27.961 --> 00:00:31.898
- I'M FINE, MARION GLASS.
- GOOD.

00:00:31.898 --> 00:00:33.766
WELL, I HAVE SOME NEWS
THAT MIGHT MAKE YOU FEEL

00:00:33.766 --> 00:00:35.634
A LITTLE BETTER, HUH?

00:00:35.634 --> 00:00:38.871
WE AT THE MAKE A WISH FOUNDATION
MAKE DREAMS COME TRUE

00:00:38.871 --> 00:00:43.743
FOR LITTLE BOYS AND LITTLE GIRLS
WHO ARE VERY SICK JUST LIKE YOU.

00:00:43.743 --> 00:00:48.648
- THERE ARE NO CHILDREN
LIKE ME, MARION GLASS.

00:00:48.648 --> 00:00:50.816
- OH, OF COURSE NOT.

00:00:50.816 --> 00:00:53.486
YOU'RE ONE OF A KIND,
BUT WE'RE GONNA MAKE ANY DREAM

00:00:53.486 --> 00:00:56.055
COME TRUE
THAT YOU COULD EVER HAVE, OKAY?

00:00:56.055 --> 00:00:57.556
- ANYTHING?

00:00:57.556 --> 00:01:00.125
- THAT'S RIGHT, BUDDY.
THAT'S RIGHT.

00:01:00.125 --> 00:01:02.962
WOULD YOU LIKE TO PLAY WITH
YOUR FAVORITE BASKETBALL TEAM?

00:01:05.598 --> 00:01:08.801
WHAT ABOUT BE SUPERMAN
FOR A DAY?

00:01:08.801 --> 00:01:11.905
- I WISH TO DROWN A MAN.

00:01:11.905 --> 00:01:14.907
[eerie music]

00:01:14.907 --> 00:01:15.941
♪ 

00:01:15.941 --> 00:01:16.942
- WHAT?

00:01:16.942 --> 00:01:21.080
- TO DROWN A MAN IN THE BATHTUB.

00:01:21.080 --> 00:01:24.350
TO HOLD HIM DOWN
WHILE THE LAST BREATH

00:01:24.350 --> 00:01:28.688
ESCAPES HIS BODY,
AND THEN BATHE IN THAT WATER,

00:01:28.688 --> 00:01:30.356
ALL THE WHILE SINGING,

00:01:30.356 --> 00:01:34.360
♪ LA-LA, LA-LA 

00:01:34.360 --> 00:01:36.696
♪ LA-LA, LA 

00:01:36.696 --> 00:01:38.998
- LIAM.

00:01:38.998 --> 00:01:42.001
- YOU SAID ANYTHING.

00:01:42.001 --> 00:01:45.271
- WELL, S-SURELY WE DON'T WANT
TO HURT OTHER PEOPLE,

00:01:45.271 --> 00:01:46.806
NOW, DO WE, KIDDO?

00:01:46.806 --> 00:01:47.807
[both laugh uneasily]

00:01:47.807 --> 00:01:49.274
ANYTHING ELSE?

00:01:49.274 --> 00:01:52.978
FLY IN A HOT AIR BALLOON
OR MEET A CELEBRITY?

00:01:52.978 --> 00:01:57.684
- MY NEW WISH IS TO LEAN OVER
THE BODY OF A DYING MAN

00:01:57.684 --> 00:02:02.054
AND PUT MY LIPS ON HIS,
STEALING HIS LAST BREATH.

00:02:02.054 --> 00:02:03.389
[inhales]

00:02:03.389 --> 00:02:04.557
- LIAM.

00:02:04.557 --> 00:02:06.659
- NO ONE WILL GET HURT.

00:02:06.659 --> 00:02:07.960
- ABSOLUTELY NOT.

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.795
I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHERE YOU--

00:02:09.795 --> 00:02:13.732
- I WISH TO TAKE
ALL THE PROSTHETIC LEGS

00:02:13.732 --> 00:02:17.904
IN THE HOSPITAL
AND BIND THEM TOGETHER

00:02:17.904 --> 00:02:21.073
WITH THE DRIED FLESH
OF THE DEAD

00:02:21.073 --> 00:02:26.579
INTO A WEBBED MASSIVE CREATURE,
AND--

00:02:26.579 --> 00:02:28.414
- LIAM!

00:02:28.414 --> 00:02:31.184
I AM SO SORRY, MS. GLASS.
- IT'S ALL RIGHT.

00:02:31.184 --> 00:02:33.252
HE--HE DOESN'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S SAYING.

00:02:33.252 --> 00:02:35.154
- I WISH TO PEE
IN YOUR MOUTH.

00:02:35.154 --> 00:02:36.922
- WHAT?
- BOTH OF YOU.

00:02:36.922 --> 00:02:37.923
- MINE?

00:02:37.923 --> 00:02:39.925
- ESPECIALLY YOU.
- OH.

00:02:39.925 --> 00:02:43.363
- I WISH TO PEE
IN BOTH OF YOUR MOUTHS

00:02:43.363 --> 00:02:45.031
AS I STAND OVER YOU.

00:02:45.031 --> 00:02:47.833
I'LL NEED A GLASS OF WATER
IN TEN MINUTES.

00:02:47.833 --> 00:02:49.034
- ENOUGH,
YOU LITTLE SHIT!

00:02:49.034 --> 00:02:50.269
- DR. GUPTA!

00:02:50.269 --> 00:02:51.937
- NO.

00:02:51.937 --> 00:02:53.106
YOU ARE REPREHENSIBLE.

00:02:53.106 --> 00:02:55.207
YOU ARE EVIL.

00:02:55.207 --> 00:02:57.176
YOU ARE A DEVIL CHILD.

00:02:57.176 --> 00:02:58.577
- [whimpering]

00:02:58.577 --> 00:03:00.446
- DR. GUPTA,
HE'S NOT A DEVIL CHILD.

00:03:00.446 --> 00:03:02.115
HE'S JUST A CHILD.

00:03:02.115 --> 00:03:04.083
YOU HAVE NO BUSINESS WORKING
IN A PEDIATRIC WARD.

00:03:04.083 --> 00:03:05.785
- WHAT?
- I'M GONNA REPORT YOU.

00:03:05.785 --> 00:03:08.287
- [crying]

00:03:08.287 --> 00:03:09.289
[door slams]

00:03:11.524 --> 00:03:16.195
- ♪ SHAME ON YOU, GUPTA 

00:03:16.195 --> 00:03:20.566
♪ SHAME ON YOU, GUPTA 

00:03:20.566 --> 00:03:24.370
YOU REALLY UPSET
MARION GLASS.

00:03:24.370 --> 00:03:29.242
- THIS IS INSANE.

00:03:29.242 --> 00:03:32.078
YOU'VE MADE ME QUESTION
EVERYTHING THAT I'VE EVER

00:03:32.078 --> 00:03:36.716
BELIEVED ABOUT THE
ESSENTIAL GOODNESS OF CHILDREN.

00:03:36.716 --> 00:03:41.987
- WISH GRANTED.

00:03:41.987 --> 00:03:45.425
[flatlining]

00:03:57.837 --> 00:04:00.906
- [gasps]
- [giggles]

00:04:00.906 --> 00:04:02.408
I AM DYING THOUGH.

00:04:02.408 --> 00:04:03.843
[flatlining]

